!.env.example
```

## Appendix B. Worker deployment shape

### `apps/api-worker/wrangler.jsonc`

```jsonc
{
  "name": "opsui-meets-api",
  "main": "src/index.ts",
  "compatibility_date": "2026-03-26",
  "workers_dev": false,
  "routes": [
    {
      "pattern": "api.opsuimeets.com/*",
      "custom_domain": true
    }
  ],
