## Appendix C. First package ownership

| Package/app | First implementation responsibility |
| --- | --- |
| `packages/shared-types` | Core enums, DTOs, event contracts, route-safe identifiers |
| `packages/config` | Environment parsing, route maps, feature flags |
| `packages/db` | Schema, migration runner, repositories |
| `apps/auth-worker` | Session lifecycle, join-token issuing, magic-link flow |
| `apps/api-worker` | Rooms, meetings, attendance, recordings APIs |
| `apps/realtime-worker` | WebSocket upgrade, room Durable Object dispatch |
| `apps/web` | Public gateway, prejoin, dashboard, live-room shell |
| `apps/admin` | Workspace policies, analytics, audit views |
| `packages/media-adapter` | Provider-facing media session and recording abstraction |

